  "detailed_description": "Mycelium is a turn-based RPG, set in the world of constant, non-ending war between two world capitals. A group of wanderers meet in the ancient cave system Mycelium, infamous among citizens. Glory, wisdom and treasures await adventurers there, though not everyone is able of carrying them outside. Main cast of diverse characters, driven by their conflicting motives, try to pull through and escape the Mycelium.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/e8027661a3edd8ee32721893820a6ef2.poster.avif?t=1729584466\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/e8027661a3edd8ee32721893820a6ef2.webm?t=1729584466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/e8027661a3edd8ee32721893820a6ef2.mp4?t=1729584466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/b00df30dd49048be0fe81e0abc8d3304.poster.avif?t=1729584466\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/b00df30dd49048be0fe81e0abc8d3304.webm?t=1729584466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/b00df30dd49048be0fe81e0abc8d3304.mp4?t=1729584466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Gameplay and storyline influence each other equally, with mechanic elements changing from story events and fate of characters being altered by your strategic decisions. Relationships between characters are created from your actions in battle and affect their behavior in certain ways.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/f90b2284ce8831eb1ad799a473a2bc06.poster.avif?t=1729584466\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/f90b2284ce8831eb1ad799a473a2bc06.webm?t=1729584466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/f90b2284ce8831eb1ad799a473a2bc06.mp4?t=1729584466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/9685e16584b4e77c0b79281854257cb2.poster.avif?t=1729584466\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/9685e16584b4e77c0b79281854257cb2.webm?t=1729584466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/9685e16584b4e77c0b79281854257cb2.mp4?t=1729584466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Character's unique abilities require completing quick mini-games, they represent direct actions your characters take to cast magic, lockpick or play lute!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/31b19f391bb0e166506b621708747c64.poster.avif?t=1729584466\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/31b19f391bb0e166506b621708747c64.webm?t=1729584466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/31b19f391bb0e166506b621708747c64.mp4?t=1729584466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/8effb8a34b9b71d1b93118071bc70ebd.poster.avif?t=1729584466\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/8effb8a34b9b71d1b93118071bc70ebd.webm?t=1729584466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/8effb8a34b9b71d1b93118071bc70ebd.mp4?t=1729584466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/1afc677d05d2b8b2f4744b62760b24ec.poster.avif?t=1729584466\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/1afc677d05d2b8b2f4744b62760b24ec.webm?t=1729584466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/1afc677d05d2b8b2f4744b62760b24ec.mp4?t=1729584466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The battle system has enemy precedency and you are in the defensive position, managing people, who can easily fall unconscious in merely 3 hits. Do your best to survive!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/5b8fe267ed69604c65e697fa4b8fa220.poster.avif?t=1729584466\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/5b8fe267ed69604c65e697fa4b8fa220.webm?t=1729584466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897730/extras/5b8fe267ed69604c